    <h3>What Is the $0 Shopify Automation Stack?</h3>
    <p>The $0 Automation Stack is a collection of six free tools that collectively replace the paid Shopify apps most stores spend $500–$900 per month on. Each tool uses a combination of <a href="https://www.make.com/en/register?pc=techie123" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Make.com</a>'s free automation tier, Google Sheets, and <a href="https://systeme.io/?sa=sa0262937272be99703a8ea16153f5dd5ae2a3eea7" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Systeme.io</a>'s free plan to achieve the same technical outcome as paid alternatives — without any monthly subscription, developer cost, or code.</p>
    <h3>Why Replace Shopify Paid Apps With Free Automation?</h3>
    <p>The core problem most Shopify stores face is that the app ecosystem is structured around recurring revenue. Tracking apps charge $149–$299/month for server-side conversion data. Inventory apps charge $29–$199/month for real-time stock syncing. Email platforms like Klaviyo charge $150–$400/month for email automations that most stores never use at full capability. <strong>The $0 stack achieves the same technical outcomes — server-side tracking, live inventory, email automation, TikTok Events API, and real-time P&L — using free tiers of tools built for automation at scale.</strong></p>
    <h3>Free Shopify Tracking — How CAPI Shield Works</h3>
    <p><a href="https://www.stackarchitect.xyz/capi-shield">CAPI Shield</a> uses Make.com to route Shopify order webhooks directly to Meta Conversions API and Google Enhanced Conversions server-to-server. iOS restrictions, ad blockers, and cookie expiry cannot intercept server-side signals. Stores typically recover 20–40% of conversion data that was previously invisible to their ad platforms — improving ROAS attribution without paying $149–$299/month for a third-party tracking tool.</p>
    <h3>Free TikTok Server-Side Tracking for Shopify</h3>
    <p>The same Make.com scenario can branch to <a href="https://www.stackarchitect.xyz/tiktok-events-api-shopify">TikTok's Events API</a> simultaneously. TikTok uses CompletePayment as its purchase event name. The server-side signal bypasses iOS ITP and ad blockers, achieving EMQ scores of 6–8 in most Shopify deployments — the same technical outcome as WeltPixel at $39/month or Analyzify at $99/month, at $0.</p>
    <h3>Free Klaviyo Alternative — Systeme.io</h3>
    <p>Klaviyo changed its billing model in February 2025 — stores now pay for every active profile whether they email them or not. <a href="https://www.stackarchitect.xyz/replace-klaviyo-free">Systeme.io's free plan</a> includes 2,000 contacts with unlimited email sends, full automation sequences, sales funnels, CRM, and affiliate management. For stores not using Klaviyo's advanced ecommerce segmentation, the migration takes 30 minutes and saves $150–$400/month permanently.</p>
    <h3>Free Shopify P&L Reporting — Live Google Sheets Dashboard</h3>
    <p>Most Shopify stores have no real-time visibility into profit — just revenue. <a href="https://www.stackarchitect.xyz/shopify-profit-loss-automation">P&L Auto</a> uses a Make.com webhook to auto-populate a Google Sheets dashboard with revenue, COGS, fees, and net profit for every order the instant payment confirms. No BI tool, no paid dashboard app, no manual exports. Replaces TrueProfit and BeProfit at $0/month.</p>
    <h3>Free Shopify Automation Without Google Script Crashes</h3>
    <p>High-volume Shopify stores running Google Apps Script automations hit quota limits that silently kill workflows mid-month. <a href="https://www.stackarchitect.xyz/autocrat-quota-fix">Autocrat Quota Fix</a> prevents this — batch processing design and trigger architecture that keeps the entire free stack running reliably at any order volume.</p>
    <h3>Free Shopify Automation Guides</h3>
    <p>The <a href="https://www.stackarchitect.xyz/shopify-automation-guides">complete guide library</a> covers every tool in the stack with step-by-step setup instructions. The most-read guides are <a href="https://www.stackarchitect.xyz/blog/shopify-server-side-tracking-complete-setup-guide">Shopify server-side tracking setup</a>, <a href="https://www.stackarchitect.xyz/blog/replace-shopify-stocky-with-a-0-inventory-system">replacing Stocky before the August 2026 shutdown</a>, and <a href="https://www.stackarchitect.xyz/blog/free-klaviyo-alternative-shopify-2026">the only truly free Klaviyo alternative for Shopify</a>.</p>
